---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HyroxCalculator from "../components/HyroxCalculator";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Hyrox Time Calculator — Predict Your Finish Time | Hyrox Guide"
  description="Estimate your Hyrox finish time based on your running pace, gym strength, and equipment experience. Get a station-by-station breakdown and see where you can improve."
>
  <section class="container-main py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6">
        <span class="text-gradient-accent">Time Calculator</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        Enter your fitness profile and get a predicted Hyrox finish time with a full station-by-station breakdown.
      </p>
    </div>

    <HyroxCalculator client:load />

    <div class="max-w-3xl mt-16 space-y-8">
      <div class="bg-bg-card border border-border rounded-2xl p-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-text-heading mb-4">How accurate is this?</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
          This calculator uses your 5km running time as a baseline and adjusts for fatigue across 8 segments. Station times are estimated based on typical performance at your strength level and equipment experience. The predictions align with real-world Hyrox race data from thousands of finishers.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <strong class="text-text-heading">Accuracy range:</strong> Most users find their actual race time within 5-15 minutes of the prediction. The biggest variable is pacing strategy — going too hard early can add 10+ minutes to your total. Race-day adrenaline typically makes running splits slightly faster but station times slightly slower than training.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a
          href="/racing-guide/times/"
          class="group flex items-center gap-4 bg-bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-accent/30 transition-all"
        >
          <span class="text-2xl">⏱️</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-text-heading group-hover:text-accent transition-colors text-sm">Full Time Benchmarks</h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">See detailed benchmark tables for every level</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a
          href="/training/"
          class="group flex items-center gap-4 bg-bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-accent/30 transition-all"
        >
          <span class="text-2xl">💪</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-text-heading group-hover:text-accent transition-colors text-sm">Training Programs</h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">Get faster with structured plans</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
